                <a name="whyblu"></a>
                                    <section class="post_content mod-bullet-copy row">
                        <div class="relatedContent col-lg-12">
                            <!--<h2>Why blu?</h2>-->
                            <h2>blu Leads the Pack</h2>
<p><img class="alignright thumbnail wp-image-5288" alt="blu PLUS+ Rechargeable Kit" src="http://d1l554c703zm4j.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/blu-plus-kit-560-417.png" width="560" height="417" /></p>
<p>blu eCigs® electronic cigarettes are the best on the market. We offer the ideal combo of quality, variety and convenience. Shop blu and find a lot of good stuff to choose from—all of it designed to be savored on the go.</p>
<ul>
<li>More options to match your lifestyle. Not ready to commit? Try our disposables. Ready to settle down? Choose from one of our rechargeable options.</li>
<li>Want tried-and-true tobacco or menthol? Got ’em. Want to try something different? We’ve got those, too.</li>
<li>The ability to recharge anytime, anywhere. Use the wall charger, USB charger, or your blu eCigs pack to charge your batteries*.</li>
<li>Long-lasting flavor. Depending on the type of vapor cigarette you choose, you can expect to get 250–400 puffs.</li>
</ul>
<address><strong>*Note:</strong>  The blu car charger is compatible with the blu Rechargeable, blu Premium, and blu Premium100 Packs. A car charger for the blu PLUS Pack will be available soon.</address>
                            <p><a href="http://www.blucigs.com/how-blu-works/why-blu/" class="btn-box">All you need to know</a></p>
                        </div>
                    </section>
                <!-- end why blu section -->
               
